            </p>
            <h3 align = "center"><img src = "/createaccount.JPG" width = "400" height = "200"></h3>
            <p>To enter your MetaMask wallet address simply click the copy icon and paste it into the corresponding text field when registering your account.</p>
            <h3 align = "center"><img src = "/copyaddress.JPG" width = "300" height = "400"></h3>
